title: Top Places to visit in Ranga Reddy, Shamshabad, Telangana
content: Ranga Reddy district, abbreviated as, R R district and also known as Cyberabad district and formerly known as Hyderabad Rural, is one of the 33 districts in the Indian state of Telangana.
